Example: Write the MultiArray out_multi_array to file. Change the current directory to "/group" and read in the same MultiArray as in_multi_array. HDF5Filefile("/path/to/file",HDF5File::New);
file.mkdir("group");
file.write("/group/dataset",out_multi_array);

file.cd("/group");
file.read("dataset",in_multi_array);
